rows.label: qst003205_msg0001
rows.name: Alulu, you all right? Not hurt?

rows.label: qst003205_msg0002
rows.name:
Alulu just happy to see
Bonono safe too!

rows.label: qst003205_msg0006
rows.name:
Alulu met Blade soon after got
separated from Bonono.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0007
rows.name:
Was running scared from monsters,
when Core Crystal fall from above!

rows.label: qst003205_msg0008
rows.name:
Alulu think, ooh, what pretty stone,
would like to give as present to friends.
So reach out and grab crystal.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0009
rows.name: But then Crystal resonate with Alulu!

rows.label: qst003205_msg0010
rows.name:
Blade appear out of nowhere
and protect Alulu from monsters!

rows.label: qst003205_msg0013
rows.name:
Anyway, staying here dangerous.
Probably should go somewhere safer.

rows.label: qst003205_msg0014
rows.name:
What? Friend Aki send Driver friends
here because worried about Bonono?

rows.label: qst003205_msg0016
rows.name:
Time to go back to Port Anangham
in Superbia and find Aki then!
